n 8 Gen 3 processor. It comes with 12GB of RAM. The Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra runs Android 14 and  is powered by a 5000mAh non-removable battery.  The Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra supports wireless charging. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra on the rear packs a quad camera setup featuring a 200-megapixel (f/1.8) primary  camera;  a 12-megapixel (f/2.2, ultra wide-angle)  camera;  a 50-megapixel (f/3.4, telephoto)  camera, and  a 10-megapixel (f/2.4)  camera. The rear camera setup has multi directional pdaf. It has a single front camera setup for selfies, featuring  a 12-megapixel sensor with an f/2.2 aperture.The Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra runs One UI 6.1 is based on Android 14 and packs 256GB, 512GB, 1TB of inbuilt storage. The Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra is a dual-SIM (GSM and GSM) mobile that accepts Nano-SIM and Nano-SIM cards. The Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra measures 162.30 x 79.00 x 8.60mm (height x width x thickness)  and weighs 232.00 grams. It was launched in Titanium Gray, Titanium Black, and  Titanium Violet colours. It features an IP68 rating for dust and water protection. Connectivity options on the Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra include Wi-Fi  802.11 a/b/g/n/ac/ax, GPS, Bluetooth v5.30, NFC, USB Type-C, Wi-Fi Direct, 3G, 4G (with support for Band 40 used by some LTE networks in India) , and  5G with active 4G on both SIM cards. Sensors on the  phone include  accelerometer,  ambient light sensor,  barometer,  compass/ magnetometer,  gyroscope,  in-display fingerprint sensor,  proximity sensor, and  fingerprint sensor. Brand exclusive features include Titanium frame, Corning Gorilla Armor (Rear and Front Panel).As of 22nd January 2025, Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra price in India starts at Rs. 99,999.','6.80-inch','Snapdragon 8 Gen 3','12MP','200MP + 12MP + 50MP + 10MP','12GB','256GB, 512GB, 1TB','5000mAh','Android 14',9.7,9.6,9.8,9.8,8.1,9.8,NULL,99999,NULL,'Samsung','Galaxy S24 Ultra',99999,'17th January 2024',NULL,'Touchscreen',NULL,NULL,'162.